'''愛德華·-{zh-tw:哈里遜;zh-hk:夏里遜;zh-cn:哈里森;}-·諾頓'''<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.edward-norton.org/faqs.html | title=Edward Norton — Frequently Asked Questions | accessdate=2006-12-19 | publisher=Edward Norton.org | archive-date=2010-04-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100418005421/http://www.edward-norton.org/faqs.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>（{{lang-en|Edward Harrison Norton}}，{{bd|1969年8月18日}}）是一名[[美國|美國]]籍男[[演員|演員]]、電影[[導演|導演]]與[[製作|製片人]]。他在1996年參與演出[[律政劇|律政劇]]《[[一級恐懼|-{zh-cn:一级恐惧; zh-hk:一級恐懼; zh-tw:驚悚;}-]]》，獲得[[奧斯卡最佳男配角獎|奧斯卡最佳男配角獎]]的提名；兩年後，他則以領銜主演光頭黨的《[[美國X檔案|美國X檔案]]》獲得[[奧斯卡最佳男主角獎|奧斯卡最佳男主角獎]]提名。他的其它代表作還有《[[鬥陣俱樂部|鬥陣俱樂部]]》、《[[紅龍|紅龍]]》和《[[無敵浩克|無敵浩克]]》。除此之外，諾頓也嘗試導演電影與編劇，並在2000年推出首次執導的電影《[[相信愛情_(美國電影)|-{zh-hk:男人愛美神; zh-tw:相信愛情; zh-cn:男人愛美神;}-]]》。

在私人領域，諾頓是位環保及社會運動者，他是非營利組織「企業社群夥伴」（Enterprise Community Partners）的受託人董事會成員及終身受託人，這個組織由他的外祖父詹姆斯·勞斯（James Rouse）所創建發展；他也是「馬賽野生保育信託基金會」（Maasai Wilderness Conservation Trust）的美國分支主席<ref>{{cite news |first=Doug |last=Gross |title=Edward Norton plays marathon man to fund African conservation |publisher=CNN |url=http://www.cnn.com/2009/SHOWBIZ/09/10/ed.norton.marathon/index.html |accessdate=2009-12-01 |date=2009-09-10 |archive-date=2010-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100407230646/http://www.cnn.com/2009/SHOWBIZ/09/10/ed.norton.marathon/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，曾在2009年參加紐約馬拉松大會為基金會募款<ref name="#1">{{cite web |title=Edward Norton to Run ING New York City Marathon with Maasai Warriors |url=http://www.nycmarathon.org/norton_release.htm |publisher=[[New_York_City_Marathon|New York City Marathon]] |accessdate=2009-12-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090914104218/http://www.nycmarathon.org/norton_release.htm |archivedate=2009年9月14日 }}</ref>，也曾經由微募款的[[社交網路服務|社群網站]]「Crowdrise」進行慈善募捐活動<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.crowdrise.com/edwardnorton | title=Edward Norton on Crowdrise | accessdate=2010-03-08 | archive-date=2015-11-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151123183558/https://www.crowdrise.com/edwardnorton | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2010年七月，[[聯合國秘書長|聯合國秘書長]][[潘基文|潘基文]]派任諾頓為聯合國親善大使<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.un.org/apps/news/story.asp?NewsID=35270&Cr=biodiversity&Cr1= | title=UN names actor Edward Norton as celebrity advocate for preserving biodiversity | accessdate=2010-07-08 | archive-date=2010-07-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100712080503/http://www.un.org/apps/news/story.asp?NewsID=35270&Cr=biodiversity&Cr1= | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 早年簡歷 ==

愛德華·諾頓生於[[麻省|麻省]][[波士頓|波士頓]]，成長於[[馬里蘭州|馬里蘭州]]的哥倫比亞<ref>{{cite web |url=http://radioalice.radio.com/2010/10/01/podcast-sarah-vinnie-october-1st/ |title=PODCAST: Sarah & Vinnie October 1st « Alice@97.3 San Francisco |publisher=Radioalice.radio.com |date=2010-10-01 |accessdate=2010-10-12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110715145031/http://radioalice.radio.com/2010/10/01/podcast-sarah-vinnie-october-1st/ |archivedate=2011年7月15日 }}</ref>，父親小愛德華·莫沃爾·諾頓（Edward Mower Norton, Jr.）是名環保[[律師|律師]]，倡導保護[[亞洲|亞洲]]的自然資源，曾在[[吉米·卡特|卡特總統]]任內擔任[[聯邦政府|聯邦]][[檢察官|檢察官]]。母親莉迪亞·羅賓森（Lydia Robinson）為英文教師，1997年因[[腦癌|腦癌]]去世<ref name="HelloMagProfile">{{cite web |url=http://www.hellomagazine.com/profiles/edward-norton/ |title=Latest news and profile of Edward Norton |publisher=hellomagazine.com |date= |accessdate=2010-10-12 |archive-date=2013-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130911075416/http://www.hellomagazine.com/profiles/edward-norton/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=dner>{{cite news|last=|first=|coauthors=|title=Miss Lydia Rouse Wed|pages=|publisher=The Baltimore Sun|date=1966-05-15|url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/baltsun/access/1795683702.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:AI&type=historic&date=May+15%2C+1966&author=&pub=The+Sun+(1837-1985)&desc=Miss+Lydia+Rouse+Wed&pqatl=google|accessdate=2010-07-10|archive-date=2012-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120111230707/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/baltsun/access/1795683702.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:AI&type=historic&date=May+15%2C+1966&author=&pub=The+Sun+(1837-1985)&desc=Miss+Lydia+Rouse+Wed&pqatl=google|dead-url=no}}</ref>。外祖父{{link-en|詹姆斯·勞斯|James Rouse}}是都市開發設計師，不但設計開發了[[馬里蘭州|馬里蘭州]]的哥倫比亞城市，也曾協助發展[[巴爾的摩|巴爾的摩]]的內港、[[維吉尼亞州|維吉尼亞州]][[諾福克_(維吉尼亞州)|諾福克市]]的濱岸市集以及[[波士頓|波士頓]]的[[昆西市場|昆西市場]]；他還和諾頓的外祖繼母派蒂·勞斯（Patty Rouse）一同創立{{link-en|企業社群合夥組織|Enterprise Community Partners}}<ref name="HelloMagProfile" /><ref name="yahoo" />。諾頓有一個弟弟和妹妹，是他的專業合作夥伴<ref name="yahoo">{{cite web|url=http://movies.yahoo.com/movie/contributor/1800018634/bio|title=Edward Norton Biography|accessdate=2008-07-05|publisher=Yahoo!|archive-date=2008-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081208191157/http://movies.yahoo.com/movie/contributor/1800018634/bio|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1981年到1985年，青少年時期的諾頓和弟弟年年參與位於[[新罕布夏州|新罕布夏州]]{{link-en|希伯倫 (新罕布什爾州)|Hebron, New Hampshire|希伯倫鎮}}（{{link-en|紐芬德湖|Newfound Lake}}畔的帕斯昆尼成長營（Camp Pasquaney）活動<ref name="yahoo" />，1984年贏得活動獎盃，後來參與營區事務兩年，導演劇場，他一直與該營區保持親密良好的關係<ref name="HelloMagProfile" /><ref name="yahoo" />。諾頓在[[美國聖公會|美國聖公會]]的背景中成長<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thisislondon.co.uk/film/article-560998-ed-takes-a-leap-of-faith.do|title=Ed takes a leap of faith|publisher=[[Evening_Standard|Evening Standard]]|date=2000-09-13|accessdate=2010-09-11|first=James|last=Mottram}}</ref>，1987年在哥倫比亞的高中畢業後就讀[[耶魯大學|耶魯大學]]<ref name="yahoo" />，期間擔任划船隊划手<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.cnn.com/2009/SHOWBIZ/09/10/ed.norton.marathon/index.html | work=CNN | title=Edward Norton plays marathon man to fund African conservation | date=2009-09-10 | accessdate=2012-12-16 | archive-date=2010-04-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100407230646/http://www.cnn.com/2009/SHOWBIZ/09/10/ed.norton.marathon/index.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>，曾與[[榮·利文斯通|榮·利文斯通]]和[[保罗·吉亚玛提|保罗·吉亚玛提]]一起積極參與戲劇活動<ref name="yahoo" />。1991年諾頓畢業取得歷史學士學位<ref name="HelloMagProfile" /><ref name="yahoo" />後就到外祖父位[[日本|日本]][[大阪市|大阪]]的分公司擔任顧問，因此略通[[日語|日語]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.edward-norton.org/articles/vogue97.html |title=Vogue January 1997 |accessdate=2008-04-27 |publisher=Edward-Norton.org |work=[[Vogue_(magazine)|Vogue]] |archive-date=2015-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150527064146/http://www.edward-norton.org/articles/vogue97.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Norton has faith in directorial skills |url=http://search.japantimes.co.jp/cgi-bin/ff20001111a1.html |accessdate=2008-04-27 |work=Japan Times |archive-date=2012-07-20 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20120720075433/http://www.japantimes.co.jp/text/ff20001111a1.html%23.UAkOp6go9Rw |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 戲劇生涯 ==

為了展開戲劇生涯，諾頓遷往[[紐約市|紐約市]]，並開始在[[外百老匯音樂劇|外百老匯]]劇院中演出<ref name="HelloMagProfile" /><ref name="yahoo" />。1996年，諾頓在其'''第一部'''電影《[[一級恐懼|一級恐懼]]》中展現了精湛的演技，電影改編自描述由[[李察·吉爾|李察·吉爾]]飾演的律師為諾頓所飾演的輔祭辯護一宗羅馬天主教主教謀殺案。《[[娛樂周刊|娛樂周刊]]》評道：「諾頓的演出足與李察·吉爾鼎立平坐，他的謙虛收歛正可對照吉爾的華美誇張。」<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,292059,00.html|title=Stuck in Low Gere|last=Tucker|first=Ken|date=1996-04-12|work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|accessdate=2009-04-28|archive-date=2009-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090427110300/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,292059,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[奧斯汀紀事報|奧斯汀紀事報]]》的影評寫道：「在這部有心理準備的驚悚片裡，諾頓的演技與恰如其份的戲劇張力，為高潮橋段提供了戲劇娛樂。」<ref>{{cite journal|last=Macor|first=Alison|date=April 1996|title=Primal Fear|publisher=[[The_Austin_Chronicle|The Austin Chronicle]]|accessdate=2009-04-28}}</ref>，儘管影評紛紛擾擾<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/primal-fear|title=Primal Fear (1996): Reviews|date=1996-04-03|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2009-04-28|archive-date=2010-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101201040542/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/primal-fear|dead-url=no}}</ref>，諾頓還是贏得了一座[[金球獎最佳電影男配角|金球獎最佳電影男配角獎]]，並獲提名為[[奧斯卡最佳男配角|奧斯卡最佳男配角]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.goldenglobes.org/browse/member/28790|title=HFPA — Awards Search|accessdate=2008-07-05|publisher=Golden Globes|archive-date=2012-08-01|archive-url=https://archive.is/20120801120205/http://www.goldenglobes.org/browse/member/28790|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="oscars">{{cite news|url=http://theenvelope.latimes.com/factsheets/awardsdb/env-awards-db-search,0,7169155.htmlstory?searchtype=person&query=Edward+Norton&x=0&y=0|title=Edward Norton|accessdate=2008-10-14|work=Los Angeles Times|archive-date=2012-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120118220837/http://theenvelope.latimes.com/factsheets/awardsdb/env-awards-db-search,0,7169155.htmlstory?searchtype=person&query=Edward+Norton&x=0&y=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>，一鳴驚人的他自此崛起美國影壇，成為廣受認可的實力派演員。同年諾頓還參與《[[情色風暴1997|情色風暴1997]]》的配角演出。

1998年，諾頓在《[[美國X檔案|美國X檔案]]》裡出飾一名[[新納粹主義|新納粹主義者]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://movies.nytimes.com/movie/review?res=9c07e4de103cf93ba15753c1a96e958260|title=Film Review; The Darkest Chambers of a Nation's Soul|last=Maslin|first=Janet|date=1998-10-28|work=The New York Times|accessdate=2009-04-28|archive-date=2011-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110205190919/http://movies.nytimes.com/movie/review?res=9C07E4DE103CF93BA15753C1A96E958260|dead-url=no}}</ref>，《[[紐約客|紐約客周刊]]》影評指出諾頓帶給這個角色「暧昧的情慾誘惑，使其充滿吸引力」<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.newyorker.com/arts/reviews/film/american_history_x_kaye|title=The Film File — American History X|last=Denby|first=David|date=1998-11-09|work=[[The_New_Yorker|The New Yorker]]|accessdate=2009-04-28|archive-date=2012-09-09|archive-url=https://archive.today/20120909173426/http://www.newyorker.com/arts/reviews/film/american_history_x_kaye|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他為了這個角色增重30磅（13公斤）的肌肉，不過後來並沒有維持這身體態<ref name="HelloMagProfile" /><ref name="yahoo" />。《美國X檔案》獲得廣泛的正面評價<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/video/titles/americanhistoryx|title=American History X (1998): Reviews|date=1998-10-30|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2009-04-28|archive-date=2010-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100422191240/http://www.metacritic.com/video/titles/americanhistoryx|dead-url=no}}</ref>，全球票房超過兩千三百萬美元<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=main&id=americanhistoryx.htm|title=American History X (1998)|date=1998-10-30|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2009-04-28|archive-date=2015-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151016214810/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=main&id=americanhistoryx.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，諾頓此角亦獲得[[奧斯卡最佳男主角|奧斯卡最佳男主角]]的提名<ref name="oscars" />。同年諾頓還和[[麥特·戴蒙|麥特·戴蒙]]共同演出《[[賭王之王|賭王之王]]》<ref>{{cite news|url=http://movies.nytimes.com/movie/review?res=980CE2DD1F3EF932A2575AC0A96E958260|title=Film Review; Knowing When to Hold 'em and Fold 'em but Just Not When to Run|last=Maslin|first=Janet|date=1998-09-11|work=The New York Times|accessdate=2009-04-28|archive-date=2012-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120210084829/http://movies.nytimes.com/movie/review?res=980CE2DD1F3EF932A2575AC0A96E958260|dead-url=no}}</ref>，飾演一對為還大筆債款而冒險涉賭的年輕人。
[[Image:Edward_Norton_By_Bridget_Laudien.jpg|thumb]]
1999年，諾頓在《[[鬥陣俱樂部|鬥陣俱樂部]]》出飾一位以旁白自稱受困於[[白領階級|白領階級]]的無名主角，電影由導演[[大衛·芬奇|大衛·芬奇]]改編自[[恰克·帕拉尼克|恰克·帕拉尼克]]的同名小說<ref name="fight">{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/books/news/9910/19/fight.club.salon/index1.html|title='Fight Club': It 'Just sort of clicked'|last=Sragow|first=Michael|date=1999-10-19|work=[[Salon.com|Salon.com]]|publisher=CNN|page=2|accessdate=2008-12-31|archive-date=2016-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161206061834/http://www.cnn.com/books/news/9910/19/fight.club.salon/index1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，諾頓為這部片子事先學習了[[拳擊|拳擊]]、[[摔角|摔角]]和[[跆拳道|跆拳道]]<ref>{{cite journal | first=Stephen | last=Garrett | url= | title=Freeze Frame | journal=[[Details_(magazine)|Details]] |date=July 1999}}</ref>。《鬥陣俱樂部》在[[威尼斯影展|威尼斯影展]]首映<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/archives/entertainment/1999/10/15/1999-10-15__fight_club__steps_into_the_.html|title='Fight Club' Steps into the Ring new Film's taking a beating for its Hyper-Violent content|last=Dominguez|first=Robert|date=1999-10-15|work=[[Daily_News_(New_York)|Daily News (New York)]]|accessdate=2008-12-07}} {{Dead link|date=April 2012|bot=H3llBot}}</ref>期間，諾頓為宣傳電影說道：「我認為《鬥陣俱樂部》在某種程度上…探討了人們對於承接這套由廣告催生的價值體系，所感受到的麻痺與絕望。」<ref>{{cite news | first=Stephen | last=Schaefer | url=http://mrshowbiz.go.com/celebrities/interviews/509_1.html | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20010417125217/http://mrshowbiz.go.com/celebrities/interviews/509_1.html | archivedate=2001年4月17日 | title=Brad Pitt & Edward Norton | work=MrShowbiz.com | accessdate=2009-04-28 | date=October 1999 | deadurl=yes }}</ref>上映後電影票房未達期望<ref name="earnings">{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/people/chart/?view=Actor&id=edwardnorton.htm|title=Edward Norton Movie Box Office Results|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2009-04-28|archive-date=2019-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190527111701/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/people/chart/?view=Actor&id=edwardnorton.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，評價兩極<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/video/titles/fightclub|title=Fight Club (1999): Reviews|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2008-12-07|date=1999-10-15|archive-date=2010-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100514102209/http://www.metacritic.com/video/titles/fightclub|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但在[[DVD|DVD]]發行後地位卻儼然斗升成為[[邪典電影|邪典]]經典<ref>{{cite news|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2004/SHOWBIZ/Movies/03/23/cult.films/|title=The personality of cult|last=Nunziata|first=Nick|date=2004-03-23|publisher=[[CNN|CNN: Showbiz/Movies]]|accessdate=2009-03-29|archive-date=2007-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071208193757/http://edition.cnn.com/2004/SHOWBIZ/Movies/03/23/cult.films/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，到了2008年，此片更被英國《[[帝國雜誌|帝國雜誌]]》提名為有史以來最佳五百大電影的前十名。

2002年，諾頓參與演出[[布萊特·拉特納|布萊特·拉特納]]的《[[紅龍|紅龍]]》和[[史派克·李|史派克·李]]的《[[25小時|25小時]]》<ref name="yahoo" />。《紅龍》評價不一，但是票房不錯<ref name="yahoo" />。《25小時》大獲好評，尤其是在紐約後[[911事件|911]]的審視氛圍下，可惜無法達到收支平衡<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0307901/business | title=Box Office/Business | accessdate=2007-09-06 | publisher=IMDB.com | archive-date=2010-01-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100113205432/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0307901/business | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Jeff|last=Stark|url=http://dir.salon.com/story/ent/movies/review/2002/12/20/25th_hour/index.html|title=25th Hour|accessdate=2008-07-05|date=2002-12-20|publisher=[[Salon.com|Salon.com]]|archive-date=2008-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080616153542/http://dir.salon.com/story/ent/movies/review/2002/12/20/25th_hour/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2003年，[[派拉蒙|派拉蒙]]以法律脅迫諾頓履行當年拍攝《一级恐惧》時簽下的三片契約，也就是後來的《[[天羅盜網|天羅盜網]]》，因此電影上映時他拒絕宣傳<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://articles.latimes.com/2008/jun/13/entertainment/et-norton13 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-12-17 |archive-date=2013-02-22 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6EdIvil3G?url=http://articles.latimes.com/2008/jun/13/entertainment/et-norton13 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="guardian.co.uk">{{Cite web |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/culture/2008/jun/14/film.features |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-12-17 |archive-date=2012-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121218034805/http://www.guardian.co.uk/culture/2008/jun/14/film.features |dead-url=no }}</ref>。諾頓在2005年的《[[天国王朝|天国王朝]]》飾演[[耶路撒冷王國|耶路撒冷王國]]國王[[鮑德溫四世|鮑德溫四世]]而備受好評<ref>{{cite web |first=Jack |last=Moore |title=Kingdom of Heaven: Director's Cut DVD Review |url=http://www.themovieinsider.com/reviews/rid/615/Kingdom_of_Heaven |accessdate=2008-07-05 |publisher=The Movie Insider |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080622000000/http://www.themovieinsider.com/reviews/rid/615/Kingdom_of_Heaven |archivedate=2008年6月22日 }}</ref>。隨後參與2008年[[漫威工作室|漫威工作室]]的《[[無敵浩克|無敵浩克]]》的演出，飾演[[漫威漫畫|漫威漫畫]]的經典人物[[浩克_(漫畫)|浩克]]<ref name="yahoo" /><ref>{{cite news |first=Josh |last=Friedman |title=New 'Incredible Hulk' may be bigger than old one |url=http://articles.latimes.com/2008/jun/13/business/fi-projector13 |accessdate=2008-07-05 |date=2008-06-13 |work=Los Angeles Times |archive-date=2013-02-23 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6EdUa0nJ6?url=http://articles.latimes.com/2008/jun/13/business/fi-projector13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，諾頓曾試圖改變劇情路線，後來失敗頹然無功，因此拒絕宣傳<ref name="guardian.co.uk"/>，雖然一度有望演出2012年電影《[[復仇者聯盟|復仇者聯盟]]》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dailytelegraph.com.au/news/breaking-news/edward-norton-ditched-from-the-avengers-film-as-producers-criticise-actors-talent/story-e6freuyi-1225890756651 |title=Edward Norton ditched from The Avengers film |publisher=The Daily Telegraph |date=2010-07-12 |accessdate=2010-10-12 |archive-date=2012-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121114201549/http://www.dailytelegraph.com.au/news/breaking-news/edward-norton-ditched-from-the-avengers-film-as-producers-criticise-actors-talent/story-e6freuyi-1225890756651 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，不過後來還是遭到換角，浩克改由[[马克·鲁法洛|马克·鲁法洛]]飾演<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.soulculture.co.uk/blogs/scnews/mark-ruffalo-confirmed-as-the-hulk-in-the-avengers-movie-full-cast-appears-at-sdcc/ |title=Mark Ruffalo Confirmed As The Hulk In THE AVENGERS Movie |publisher=SoulCulture |date=2010-07-25 |accessdate=2010-10-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100820093050/http://www.soulculture.co.uk/blogs/scnews/mark-ruffalo-confirmed-as-the-hulk-in-the-avengers-movie-full-cast-appears-at-sdcc/ |archivedate=2010-08-20 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

2006年，諾頓主演了兩部電影《[[愛在山谷下|愛在山谷下]]》跟《[[魔幻至尊|魔幻至尊]]》，後者在[[日舞影展|日舞影展]]首映，正式上映後成為票房黑馬<ref name="yahoo" />。2008年，諾頓參演[[新線影業|新線影業]]的《[[非法警戒|非法警戒]]》，飾演一名正直警探被派任前去調查自己親哥哥所主持的警局。此片評價不甚良好，也沒有獲得電影公司的大力支持，儘管有[[柯林·法洛|柯林·法洛]]和[[強·沃特|強·沃特]]等大牌影星，全球票房還是只有三千一百一十萬美元，稍稍打平製作成本三千萬而已<ref>{{citation|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=prideandglory.htm|title=Box Office Mojo|accessdate=2011-12-15|archive-date=2011-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111219005404/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=prideandglory.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2010年，諾頓亦主演了兩部電影《[[雙子陰謀|雙子陰謀]]》與《[[色獄心機|色獄心機]]》，前者一人分飾雙胞胎（一個是小咖毒販，另一個是哈佛教授），後者找回諾頓在《[[鬼計神偷|鬼計神偷]]》合作過的老搭檔[[勞勃·狄尼洛|勞勃·狄尼洛]]，片中諾頓飾演的囚犯想方設法要詐得狄尼洛飾演的假釋官一紙提前假釋令。2012年，諾頓參與演出《[[神鬼認證4|神鬼認證4]]》。

諾頓曾在2005年的實驗電視喜劇《{{link-en|情迷絲苔拉|Stella (TV series)}}》友情客串<ref>{{cite web |first=Rob |last=Thomas |title=Media musings: The state of The State |url=http://www.madison.com/tct/features/index.php?ntid=45095&ntpid=1 |accessdate=2008-07-05 |date=2005-06-29 |publisher=The Capital Times |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081003003605/http://www.madison.com/tct/features/index.php?ntid=45095&ntpid=1 |archivedate=2008年10月3日 }}</ref>，也在2010年[[美國廣播公司|ABC電視台]]的[[艾美獎|艾美獎]]得獎片《[[摩登家庭|摩登家庭]]》中露臉。諾頓經常為他參演的作品做些不具名的編劇工作，像是《鬼計神偷》<ref name="yahoo" />、《[[揮灑烈愛|揮灑烈愛]]》<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.avclub.com/content/node/57162/2| title=Edward Norton — A.V. Club Interview| accessdate=2007-01-09| publisher=AV Club| archive-date=2007-01-07| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070107173231/http://www.avclub.com/content/node/57162/2| dead-url=no}}</ref>和《無敵浩克》<ref>{{cite news|first=Chris|last=Tookey|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/reviews/article-1026114/The-Incredible-Hulk-Trust-wont-like-.html|title=The Incredible Hulk: Trust me, you won't like him...|accessdate=2009-12-15|date=2008-06-13|work=Daily Mail|location=London|archive-date=2010-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100416082829/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/reviews/article-1026114/The-Incredible-Hulk-Trust-wont-like-.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他曾在2000年推出導演處女作《相信愛情》，並自導自演改編自[[布魯克林孤兒|同名小說]]的《[[布魯克林孤兒_(電影)|布魯克林孤兒]]》（2019年）<ref name="yahoo" /><ref>{{cite web|first=Andy|last=Lea|url=http://www.dailystar.co.uk/news/view/40181/Hulk-star-Ed-s-Incredible-Sulk/|title=Hulk Star Ed's Incredible Hulk|accessdate=2008-07-05|date=2008-06-08|work=Daily Star|archive-date=2009-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090604212739/http://www.dailystar.co.uk/news/view/40181/Hulk-star-Ed-s-Incredible-Sulk/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。諾頓性格以其完美主義聞名，曾主導剪輯《美國X檔案》的最終版本，拍攝《紅龍》期間與導演發生衝突，在拍攝《無敵浩克》時也與導演和電影公司衝突，導致拒絕為此片宣傳<ref>{{cite news|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2008/jun/13/entertainment/et-norton13|title=A history of flexing his muscles|last=Lee|first=Chris|date=2008-06-13|work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|accessdate=2012-12-04|archive-date=2013-02-22|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6EdIvil3G?url=http://articles.latimes.com/2008/jun/13/entertainment/et-norton13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 私人領域 ==
[[File:Ed_Norton_Shankbone_Metropolitan_Opera_2009.jpg|thumb]]
諾頓極不習慣明星光芒，他說：「要我放棄搭地鐵，不如讓我心臟病發。」<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.edward-norton.org/articles/vogue97.html| title=Wanted: Edward Norton| publisher=''[[Vogue_(magazine)|Vogue]]''| author=Handelman, David| date=January 1997| accessdate=2008-04-28| archive-date=2015-05-27| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150527064146/http://www.edward-norton.org/articles/vogue97.html| dead-url=no}}</ref>他曾在訪問中表示自己是[[巴爾的摩金鶯|巴爾的摩金鶯隊]]的球迷<ref name="orioles">{{cite web|first=Roch|last=Kubatko|title=New Stage for Norton|url=http://www.edward-norton.org/events/newstage.html|accessdate=2008-07-05|date=2001-07-08|work=[[Baltimore_Sun|Baltimore Sun]]|archive-date=2010-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100427003014/http://www.edward-norton.org/events/newstage.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並在2001年受邀參與鐵人[[小卡爾·瑞普肯|小卡爾·瑞普肯]]的退休活動，2007年七月出席瑞普肯在名人堂的慶祝儀式<ref>{{cite web|first=Elizabeth M.|last=Botello|title=TWIB devotes show to Ripken, Gwynn|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20070726&content_id=2110658&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb|accessdate=2008-07-05|date=2007-07-26|publisher=MLB.com|archive-date=2012-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121105084805/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20070726&content_id=2110658&vkey=news_mlb&fext=.jsp&c_id=mlb|dead-url=no}}</ref>。諾頓擁有[[私人飛行執照|私人飛行執照]]，曾在《[[大衛深夜秀|大衛深夜秀]]》和《{{link-en|演員內心秀|Inside the Actor's Studio}}》節目上談論他的飛行訓練課程<ref>{{cite episode |title=Inside the Actors Studio — Edward Norton |series=Inside the Actors Studio |network=Bravo |airdate=2003-01-12 |season=9 |number=906}}</ref>。諾頓與歌手[[寇特妮·洛芙|寇特妮·洛芙]]和女演員[[莎瑪·海耶克|莎瑪·海耶克]]約會過<ref>{{cite news|title=Edward Norton: Man of pride and glory|date=2008-11-15|url=http://www.halesowennews.co.uk/newsxtra/3828972.Edward_Norton__Man_of_pride_and_glory/newspaper=Halesowen News|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130526155123/http://www.halesowennews.co.uk/newsxtra/3828972.Edward_Norton__Man_of_pride_and_glory/newspaper=Halesowen/|archivedate=2013年5月26日|df=}}</ref>，現在已和製片人莎娜·羅柏森（Shauna Robertson）訂婚。

在政治與公眾事務上，諾頓是前[[紐約州州長|紐約州州長]][[艾略特·斯皮策|艾略特·斯皮策]]的有力支持者<ref>{{cite news|first=Danny|last=Hakim|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/01/16/nyregion/16campaign.html|title=As Spitzer's Popularity Fell, Donors Rallied to His Side|accessdate=2008-07-05|date=2008-01-16|work=[[The_New_York_Times|New York Times]]|archive-date=2013-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131220093348/http://www.nytimes.com/2008/01/16/nyregion/16campaign.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他是非營利組織{{tsl|en|Enterprise Community Partners|企業社群合夥組織}}的董事成員，為家鄉建設提供一般人負擔得起的經濟住屋。他對環保事務與可再生能源方面的關注也相當為人所知，像是企業綠色社區計畫（Enterprise's Green Communities Initiative）和[[BP|BP]]的「太陽能鄰居」方案<ref>{{cite web|title=Ed Norton, BP Solar and the High Line|url=http://www.treehugger.com/files/2004/11/ed_norton_bp_so_1.php|accessdate=2008-07-05|publisher=Treehugger.com|archive-date=2010-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100325101614/http://www.treehugger.com/files/2004/11/ed_norton_bp_so_1.php|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.solarneighbors.com/|title=Edward Norton|accessdate=2008-07-05|publisher=solarneighbors.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080828213826/http://www.solarneighbors.com/|archive-date=2008-08-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Interview with Edward Norton|url=http://www.grist.org/news/maindish/2005/04/27/little-norton/|accessdate=2008-07-05|publisher=Grist.org|archive-date=2008-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080514085930/http://www.grist.org/news/maindish/2005/04/27/little-norton/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他也投注時間金錢在社會活動事務上，包括改善[[貧窮|弱勢族群]]的生活品質<ref>{{cite web |title=Edward Norton |url=http://www.enterprisecommunity.org/local_work/california/ |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080121025737/http://www.enterprisecommunity.org/local_work/california/ |archivedate=2008年1月21日 |accessdate=2008-07-05 |publisher=Enterprise community |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Hollywood stars heat up solar power |publisher=CNN |url=http://money.cnn.com/magazines/business2/business2_archive/2006/01/01/8368105/index.htm |accessdate=2008-07-05 |date=2006-01-01 |first=Monica |last=Heger |archive-date=2006-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061111082535/http://money.cnn.com/magazines/business2/business2_archive/2006/01/01/8368105/index.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。諾頓參與監製[[HBO|HBO]]紀錄片《{{link-en|歐巴馬：白宮之路|By the People: The Election of Barack Obama}}》，此片原聲帶收益全數捐給企業社群夥伴和{{link-en|美國聯合勸募協會|United Way of America}}，他也在2008年登上《快速公司》（Fast Company）雜誌的一則講述建商提供綠色經濟住屋的專題故事。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fastcompany.com/magazine/131/edward-nortons-9000000000-housing-projects-thats-9-billion.html |title=Magazine October 2010 Issue 149 |publisher=Fast Company |date= |accessdate=2010-10-12}}</ref>。諾頓是馬賽野生保育信託基金會（Maasai Wilderness Conservation Trust）的美國分支主席<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cnn.com/2009/SHOWBIZ/09/10/ed.norton.marathon/index.html |title=Edward Norton plays marathon man to fund African conservation |publisher=CNN |date=2009-09-10 |accessdate=2009-12-01 |archive-date=2010-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100407230646/http://www.cnn.com/2009/SHOWBIZ/09/10/ed.norton.marathon/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，為了幫基金會募款，2009年11月1日諾頓帶領一行30人團隊浩浩蕩蕩參與紐約馬拉松大會<ref name="#1"/>，陣容包括有歌手[[艾拉妮絲·莫莉塞特|艾拉妮絲·莫莉塞特]]和魔術師[[大衛·布萊恩|大衛·布萊恩]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Meet the Runners |url=http://www.maasaimarathon.com/content/runners/ |publisher=Maasai Marathon |accessdate=2009-12-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120907011835/http://www.maasaimarathon.com/content/runners/ |archivedate=2012年9月7日 }}</ref>，諾頓是名流中第一個完成賽程的人，跑了3小時48分鐘<ref name="nyrr">{{cite news |first=Josh |last=Zembik |title=Fast Facts on Sunday's Record-Breaking Field |publisher=New York Road Runners |date=2009-11-02 |url=http://www.nyrrmedia.org/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=210:fast-facts-on-sundays-record-breaking-field&catid=46:fast-facts&Itemid=69 |accessdate=2009-12-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100416084732/http://www.nyrrmedia.org/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=210%3Afast-facts-on-sundays-record-breaking-field&catid=46%3Afast-facts&Itemid=69 |archivedate=2010年4月16日 }}</ref>，為基金會募得超過一百萬美元<ref name="nyrr" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.maasaimarathon.com/content/sponsor/|title=Maasai Marathon — Sponsor|accessdate=2009-12-01|publisher=Maasai Marathon|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120904110712/http://www.maasaimarathon.com/content/sponsor/|archivedate=2012年9月4日}}</ref>。2010年5月，諾頓推出一個名叫「Crowdrise」的社群網站，作為慈善募款之用<ref>{{cite news |last=Banjo |first=Shelly |url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052748703880304575236432780628948.html |title=Edward Norton's Toughest Role: Fund-Raiser - WSJ.com |publisher=Online.wsj.com |date=2010-05-11 |accessdate=2010-10-12 |archive-date=2010-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101001180354/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052748703880304575236432780628948.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

